    <note>Li(2) Ge(3) [19327] Li Fu, WJ, 8.13a-14b. His son-in-law, Qu(2) Gao [24480] has the same surname as Qu(2) Jingchun [24478], son-in-law of Gao(1) Shiqing [3448], whose funerary inscription was composed by Ge(3)'s brother, Fu(8) [19329], and Qu(2) was also the surname of Gao(1) Shiqing's second wife. The only identifiable Qu(2) lineage in CBD is a Kaifeng family of painters. There are several military Qu(2) indexed in XCB. In order to establish probable cross-cousin marriage and affinal linkages between the Li(2) and Gao(1), I am entering Qu(2) A [24479] as grandfather of Qu(2) Jingchun, who is entered as grandfather of Qu(2) Gao. CBD, 2, 885.</note>
